This was one of my favorites to come out in 1996 and was really a seemingly new sound at the 

time.  I was in Hawaii and listening to a lot of local music at the time, but what little 

music that managed to trickle into the islands was usually of high caliber.  This album not 

withstanding was one of the best of the year. I still enjoy listening to it today and hope 

you will too.

Enjoy!
